Safety Stock is the amount of left over inventory by the time the next order arrives. The variables consider are the demand for the product which is unknown but can estimated accurately with known things such as usually order amounts given time of year, etc. The Reorder Order Quanity helps in deciding the correct amount to order with not hhaving excess or too little.
Order quanity is a variable you can control - ordering enough inventory to satisfy the demand is important especially with holding and ordering costs.
Fixed cost of production is also a variable consider due to the costs it take to make the product
